ActGovernment Employees Compensation Act
SubjectPublic Private Partnerships Canada ** DECLARATION ** Officers and employees of Authority declared
PrecisOrder approving the DECLARATION made by the Minister of Labour to the effect that the officers and employees of PUBLIC PRIVATE PARTNERSHIPS CANADA are employees for the purposes of the Government Employees Compensation Act.
